{
  "stem": "11916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this day, those five girls nicely disappeared with their suitcases.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they did not catch them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They promised us everything-- double bread, everything-- where the five girls gone?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, the girls known the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we don't know where they-- even if we know, who would ever say?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we was happy for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after this-- [SIGHS] after this-- When you got to Freidenen, what happened there?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Freidenen, there was a camp where was other girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it wasn't a crematorium there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We was there for a few days, just to have a rest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Maybe four, five days, and after this, we have been gone to the trains again, with the open trains, until we reach Salzwedel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our trip in the open train was two to three weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the worst time in our life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was as bad as Auschwitz, because this time, we was in the winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We was very, very sick this time in our bodies, full of louses, full of sickness.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the cold didn't help us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] With these wagons, there was the snow, rain, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all we have is a blanket all over our head, and a group hanging together-- usually, as many as you were-- to keep you cold-- to warm.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And between the group, every morning, quite a few dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the morning when we was waked up-- we wasn't waked up, because we wasn't laying down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We was sleeping by standing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They just ask you how many dead on the morning, and that has to be thrown out from the wagon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this time, we see the bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We was close to Hanover and other places, and Hanover was burning.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
